#

Lemon Herb Grilled Chicken with Asparagus

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Grilled ChickenHealthyEasy Weeknight Dinner

Description

Juicy grilled chicken marinated in fresh herbs and zesty lemon, paired with tender asparagus for a refreshing meal.

Ingredients

  • Boneless Chicken Breast: 2 pieces
  • Fresh Lemon Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic Cloves: 2, minced
  • Fresh Rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
